<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Services</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #5f6c7b;
            background-color: #fffffe;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #094067;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #3da9fc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        footer {
            background: #094067;
            color: #fffffe;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>At Hotel Sai Manoj, we pride ourselves on offering a variety of services to satisfy your cravings, from snacks to full meals, delivered directly to your home. Below are the services we provide:</p>

        <h2>1. Online Food Delivery</h2>
        <p>Our core service is delivering freshly prepared, delicious food to your doorstep. We specialize in:
            <ul>
                <li>Cheesy and customizable pizzas</li>
                <li>Juicy and flavorful burgers</li>
                <li>Crispy and tasty snacks like samosas, vada pav, and more</li>
                <li>Refreshing beverages to complement your meals</li>
            </ul>
            You can easily browse our menu online, place an order, and enjoy fast and reliable delivery.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Customizable Orders</h2>
        <p>We understand that everyone has different preferences, which is why we allow you to customize your food. Whether you want extra toppings on your pizza or a spicier version of our vada pav, we've got you covered!</p>

        <h2>3. Bulk Orders for Events</h2>
        <p>Hosting an event? We offer bulk orders for parties, office events, or gatherings. Our team will ensure your food is delivered hot and fresh, making your event a success with delicious food options.</p>

        <h2>4. Fast and Secure Payment Options</h2>
        <p>We provide a range of payment options including credit/debit cards, UPI, and digital wallets, all secured through trusted payment gateways. Enjoy hassle-free, secure transactions every time.</p>

        <h2>5. Customer Support</h2>
        <p>If you have any issues or special requests, our customer support team is always available to assist you. Feel free to <a href="/contact">contact us</a> anytime for help with orders, payments, or general inquiries.</p>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
